&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of professional software engineering experience, with a track record of shipping and maintaining complex systems or products in production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full-stack experience with modern front-end frameworks (e.g., React/TypeScript) and back-end technologies (e.g., Ruby, Python, Go, PostgreSQL).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong collaboration and communication skills, with experience working effectively across functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;While it’s not required, it’s an added plus if you also have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with B2B SaaS, billing/payments infrastructure, developer platforms, or enterprise-scale systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with technologies such as Stripe, Salesforce, NetSuite, Snowflake, SCIM, SAML, or WebAssembly.&lt;/li&gt;
